    "text": "Hello! Would anyone be interested in an FoC book club?\n\nHere's what I'm thinking for structure (but very open to suggestions):\n\n• *What:* Read and discuss books about the history and future of programming, e.g. _<https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/722412.The_Dream_Machine|The Dream Machine>_, _<https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/581700.A_Small_Matter_of_Programming|A Small Matter of Programming>_\n• *When:* One hour meeting every other month on Zoom to discuss one book. Time TBD (timezones could be hard)\n• *How:* Anyone can nominate a book. Vote via Slack poll in <#C037X8XMFB3|reading-together> (or perhaps a new, dedicated channel)",
